name: JOKE
description: JOKE is a fun, community driven meme project on Solana, led by the witty, satirical character Dejoke. It transforms crypto and everyday absurdities into sharp, visual storytelling, proving that serious news hits harder with humor. Community driven at its core, Dejoke aims to go viral and evolve beyond just a meme into a cultural brand. “No Joke, No Life.” $JOKE powers all community decisions, content access, and creator rewards in this irreverent Web3 movement.
